item.title: First Post
item.description:
So every blog thingie needs a first post.

This is mine.

It’ll be short because it is late and also I’m running out of battery in this laptop.

But I didn’t want to succumb to my adhd for a change, and I want this new website to have at least a tiny bit of content.

So: I’ll drop some screenshots of Outpact, the font I’ve been working on for most of this year, and I’m really proud. It’s my first nice big widely useful font under my own name and I’ll be giving it away for free.
